## 严格禁止的反模式

### ❌ 反模式 #1: Service Locator

**错误示例**:
```typescript
// ❌ 绝对禁止
const executor = getServiceContainer().scriptExecutor;
```

**正确做法**:
```typescript
// ✅ 使用构造函数注入
constructor(private scriptExecutor: IScriptExecutor) {}
```

---

### ❌ 反模式 #2: 循环依赖

**错误示例**:
```typescript
// ❌ 循环依赖：Panel ↔ Handler ↔ DataProvider
class RequestTesterPanel {
  private environmentHandler = new EnvironmentHandler(this);  // ← this as context
  private dataProvider = new PanelDataProvider(environmentHandler);
  (environmentHandler as any).contextProvider = dataProvider;  // ← 后期注入，错误！
}
```

**正确做法**:
```typescript
// ✅ 通过 Factory 分离依赖
class HandlerFactory {
  static createHandlers(contextProvider: IPanelContextProvider): IMessageHandler[] {
    return [
      new EnvironmentHandler(services, contextProvider),
      new RequestExecutionHandler(services, contextProvider),
      // ... 所有初始化完成
    ];
  }
}

class RequestTesterPanel {
  private handlers = HandlerFactory.createHandlers(this.dataProvider);
}
```

---

### ❌ 反模式 #3: 共享可变状态

**错误示例**:
```typescript
// ❌ RequestContext 被多个 Handler 修改
const context = this.contextProvider.getCurrentContext();
context.request.headers = { ...headers };  // ← 修改共享对象
context.environment = selectedEnv;          // ← 又修改了
```

**正确做法**:
```typescript
// ✅ Handler 不修改状态，使用 Command 返回 DTO
const result = await this.executeCommand.execute({
  collectionId,
  requestId,
  environmentId
});

// result 是不可变的 DTO
messenger.postMessage({ type: 'success', data: result });
```

---

### ❌ 反模式 #4: 类型转换

**错误示例**:
```typescript
// ❌ 使用 as any 绕过类型检查
(this.environmentHandler as any).contextProvider = dataProvider;
this as any;  // this 类型不对
```

**正确做法**:
```typescript
// ✅ 通过接口确保类型安全
interface IContextAware {
  setContext(provider: IPanelContextProvider): void;
}

class EnvironmentHandler implements IContextAware {
  setContext(provider: IPanelContextProvider): void {
    this.contextProvider = provider;
  }
}
```

---

### ❌ 反模式 #5: Handler 负责 DI 容器

**错误示例**:
```typescript
// ❌ Handler 负责创建依赖
class RequestExecutionHandler {
  constructor(contextProvider) {
    this.scriptExecutor = getServiceContainer().scriptExecutor;
    this.requestPreparer = getServiceContainer().requestPreparer;
  }
}
```

**正确做法**:
```typescript
// ✅ Handler 只接收依赖
class RequestExecutionHandler {
  constructor(
    private scriptExecutor: IScriptExecutor,
    private requestPreparer: IRequestPreparer,
    private contextProvider: IPanelContextProvider
  ) {}
}

// 在 Factory 中创建
new RequestExecutionHandler(
  container.scriptExecutor,
  container.requestPreparer,
  contextProvider
);
```

