### Command 创建规范

所有 Command 必须遵循此模板：

```typescript
import { ICommand } from '../command.interface';
import { IOrchestrator } from '../../orchestration/interfaces';
import { IEventBus } from '../../orchestration/event-bus.interface';

/**
 * Command: [Use case description]
 * 
 * Responsibility:
 * - Validate input DTO
 * - Orchestrate workflow
 * - Publish domain events
 * - Return output DTO
 */
export interface MyCommandInput {
  collectionId: string;
  requestId: string;
  environmentId?: string;
}

export interface MyCommandOutput {
  success: boolean;
  data?: any;
  error?: string;
}

export class MyCommand implements ICommand<MyCommandInput, MyCommandOutput> {
  constructor(
    private orchestrator: IOrchestrator,   // ✅ 接口依赖
    private eventBus: IEventBus            // ✅ 事件总线
  ) {}

  async execute(input: MyCommandInput): Promise<MyCommandOutput> {
    try {
      // 1. 验证输入
      this.validateInput(input);

      // 2. 调用 Orchestrator
      const result = await this.orchestrator.execute({
        collectionId: input.collectionId,
        requestId: input.requestId
      });

      // 3. 发布事件
      this.eventBus.publish({
        type: 'myCommandExecuted',
        data: result,
        timestamp: Date.now()
      });

      // 4. 返回 DTO（不可变）
      return {
        success: true,
        data: result
      };
    } catch (error) {
      return {
        success: false,
        error: (error as Error).message
      };
    }
  }

  private validateInput(input: MyCommandInput): void {
    if (!input.collectionId) {
      throw new Error('collectionId is required');
    }
    if (!input.requestId) {
      throw new Error('requestId is required');
    }
  }
}
```

**检查清单**:
- [ ] 定义 Input/Output 接口（DTO）
- [ ] 实现 ICommand<Input, Output>
- [ ] 构造函数只接收接口
- [ ] execute() 返回 Promise<Output>（不是 void）
- [ ] 返回值是不可变的 DTO
- [ ] 调用 eventBus.publish() 发布事件
- [ ] 没有 getServiceContainer() 调用
- [ ] 涵盖计入输入验证

